title: (x) Log cabin type - various {gang}
content: Can anyone direct me to a link or give me the name of the font that looks like it is made out of branches?
author: julia

comments.content: How about [Logger](http://web.archive.org/web/20051108150626/http:/www.dafont.com/en/search.php?nq=1&q=logger)? I recall House doing a custom thing for How magazine last year that was really nice, but I don't know if they ever made it into a font.
